<br>
As far as I'm aware, the member guilds are -<br>
<br>
League of Honour<br>
Tapiolan Sankarit (European)<br>
Clan of Brothers (males only)<br>
Circle of Sisters (females only)<br>
Elven Blades (Elves and half-elves only)<br>
Saga<br>
Northern Elite (Barbarians only)<br>
Ring of the Light<br>
Lux Aeternam<br>
